{"tid":1703292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［被罷工］如果返工返學搭港鐵同巴士係幫助分流，咁同一時間搭同一種交通工具會點？","createTime":"2019-11-10T08:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T14:48:59.000Z","uid":92479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d30f61c2b688a262488d16b88b5b504d774b9f4f","tid":1703292,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:13:14.000Z","msg":"【港鐵故障】港鐵4線同時壞 港九大塞車！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/862507/lifestyle/港鐵-故障-塞車-二次創作/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F862507%2Flifestyle%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C-%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A-%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%2F&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=4838237a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/862507/lifestyle/港鐵-故障-塞車-二次創作/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵癱瘓全港仆街，代表咗城市運輸一直處於極限<br />\n<br />\n有人話香港過度依賴港鐵先會促成今日惡果，應該做好其他交通工具嘅Plan B分流云云：但其實你今日一眼睇倒，當地鐵全線慢駛一刻，幾乎全香港所有馬路隧道亦同時迫爆，就算開再多嘅接駁巴士同小巴，有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/港鐵癱瘓全港仆街-代表咗城市運輸一直處於極限-唔係單靠規劃分流可以解決-e9029d60825f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40henryporterbabe%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%BB%86%E8%A1%97-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%92%97%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E8%99%95%E6%96%BC%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90-%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E5%96%AE%E9%9D%A0%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E5%88%86%E6%B5%81%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA-e9029d60825f&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f7ca2392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@henryporterbabe/港鐵癱瘓全港仆街-代表咗城市運輸一直處於極限-唔係單靠規劃分流可以解決-e9029d60825f</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為打工仔最怕同一時間搭巴士又有交通阻塞，真係好頭㾗"},{"pid":"19a6127d138c2e7d2a1b29b6ffea60c4e9d629ab","tid":1703292,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f